	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">Anime Expo News</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Stalk</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Tue,  4 Jul 2006, 09:14:00</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=Anime%20Expo%20News&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Fnews%2FSH%2Fnews_288.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
